OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinisters to meet to       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdiscuss Post Office scandal
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers are to meet to consider      
OL,6, measures into clearing the names of    
OL,7, hundreds of sub-postmasters convicted  
OL,8, in the Post Office Horizon scandal.    
OL,10,FJustice secretary Alex Chalk will meet 
OL,11,FKevin Hollinrake, the minister for the 
OL,12,FPost Office, on Monday.                
OL,14,FIt comes after the prime minister told 
OL,15,Fthe BBC the government was reviewing   
OL,16,Foptions to help victims of the scandal.
OL,18,FMore than 700 branch managers were     
OL,19,Fconvicted of false accounting, theft   
OL,20,Fand fraud based on faulty software.    
